    {"type":"text","id":"l1t","x":150,"y":63,"width":500,"height":88,"text":"Layer 1: maxTurns\n---------------------------------------\nMeasures: Conversation turn count (configurable per agent)\nAction:   Halt when maxTurns reached -- no further model calls\nLocation: queryLoop turn counter in core/src/agent/\n\nPurpose: prevents runaway infinite conversational loops","originalText":"Layer 1: maxTurns\n---------------------------------------\nMeasures: Conversation turn count (configurable per agent)\nAction:   Halt when maxTurns reached -- no further model calls\nLocation: queryLoop turn counter in core/src/agent/\n\nPurpose: prevents runaway infinite conversational loops","fontSize":10,"fontFamily":3,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","strokeColor":"#6C63FF","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":200003,"version":1,"versionNonce":200004,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":null,"link":null,"locked":false,"containerId":"layer1","lineHeight":1.25},

